{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the application exhibits the capability to detect multiple objects simultaneously, as demonstrated in Figure 2.",
    "The image showcases a diverse scene containing various objects such as persons and bicycles.",
    "After detection, the text was converted into speech using the pyttsx module.",
    "This showed the capability to handle the various different types of objects, as well as if there are multiple of them present in a single image.In addition to its object detection and speech synthesis capabilities, the application features an advanced augmentation function facilitated by contextual cues.",
    "Upon receiving static images with accompanying context from the user, the application extends its functionality by incorporating contextual understanding into the object detection process."
  ]
}